items.title: Former Iraqi PM Maliki denounces Trump threats to end support if he returns to power
items.description: The US president said Iraq would have "zero" chance of success without American support.

items.title: Three brothers die after falling in frozen Texas pond
items.description: Their mother says she tried to rescue them by lifting them out but the ice kept breaking.

items.title: 'I don't let bullies win': US congresswoman Omar defiant after substance thrown at her
items.description: The Minnesota Democrat was uninjured and continued to speak at her event, after being sprayed with an unidentified liquid.
